<plot>Ibrahim comes to Buenos Aires on a mission of death, destruction, and martyrdom. But when he falls under the spell of a Jewish shop keeper and her family, he begins to question the hatred and revenge he harbors in his heart. Using the real-life 1994 bombing of the AMIA Jewish Center in Buenos Aires as a jumping off point, "Ablution" fictionalizes Ibrahim's journey and asks the question "what if...".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?021340</url></doc>
